- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel method for kernel computation, which is relevant to AI. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses a linear complexity algorithm for computing vectors for trees.
